'''''Kaddu Beykat''''' ( Letter from My Village cyagwa ''Lettre paysanne'' ) ni filime yo [[Senegali|muri Senegal yo mu]] 1975 iyobowe na Safi Faye . Niyo filime ya mbere yerekanwe yakozwe n’umugore wo muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara yatanzwe mu bucuruzi kandi izana amahanga ku muyobozi wayo. <ref name="NFU">Ukadike, p.30</ref> <ref name="LS">Spaas, p.185</ref> Ishingiye ku rukundo, ivuga ubuzima bwa buri munsi bw'abantu bo mucyaro cya Senegal.

== Umugambi ==
Ngor ni umusore uba mu mudugudu wa Senegali wifuza kurongora Coumba. amapfa yo mu mudugudu afite ingaruka kubihingwa, nuko Ngor ntashobore kubona  inkwano ya Columba. Yagiye mu murwa mukuru wa Senegali, Dakar, kugira ngo agerageze gushaka amafaranga menshi . Agaruka ku baturage maze abwira abandi ibyamubayeho mu mujyi. Iyi nkuru yerekana ubuzima bwa buri munsi bw'abaturage, ivuga uburyo bw'ibaruwa yandikiye inshuti ye, izwi nka Faye. <ref name="SR">Russell, p. 59</ref>

